body:
Tea crafts in Samovar.
Black tea - 1 cup, 1 black tea leaf;
Green tea - 1 cup, 1 green tea leaf;
Berry tea - 1 cup,  1 sweet berry;
Hibiscus tea - 1 cup, 1 Spore blossom;
Chamomile tea - 1 cup, 1 oxeye daisy;
In the world you can find a tea trees from which you can get black tea leaf and green tea leaf.
Added new types of tea with lemon.New structures where you can find items to upgrade your tea katana.
The Tea Katana can only shoot if you have the Tea Power effect, which you get when you drink tea
Tea katana handle - gives you a speed when tea katana hold in off hand
Samovar garda - gives you a double jump when tea katana hold in off hand
Tea tree flowers - gives durability to your tea katana and increases damage
Lemon tea is upgrade version of basic tea. It prolong effects and increases its level
